OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778253065
OL,3,CBrother of boy who drowned in Lake
OL,4,CDistrict calls for better safety
OL,5,Cregulations
OL,7,FThe brother of a teenager who drowned
OL,8,Fat a Lake District beauty spot is
OL,9,Fcalling for better safety regulations
OL,10,Faround open water.
OL,12,FAdil Ahmed spoke to ITV Border about
OL,13,Fthe death of his brother, Absi Ahmed,
OL,14,Fwho drowned at High Dam Tarn on
OL,15,FTuesday 7 April.
OL,17,FHe says that he and his family are
OL,18,Fstill processing the loss: "It feels
OL,19,Fsurreal if I am being honest. For me
OL,20,Fit still doesn't feel like my brother
OL,21,Fis gone.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778253065
OL,3,CBrother of boy who drowned in Lake
OL,4,CDistrict calls for better safety
OL,5,Cregulations
OL,7,F"When I have came here it doesn't feel
OL,8,Flike this is actually where it
OL,9,Fhappened. I don't know what the words
OL,10,Fare to say to be honest but it is a
OL,11,Fbeautiful, peaceful place. It is nice
OL,12,Fto know he was surrounded by beauty.
OL,14,F"I can't imagine what the words are,
OL,15,Fespecially for my parents. For me it
OL,16,Fis not the nature of order of things
OL,17,Fhaving to bury your own child. It is
OL,18,Fsomething we will never ever forget.
OL,19,FWe have lost someone and the house
OL,20,Ffeels very empty now."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778253065
OL,3,CBrother of boy who drowned in Lake
OL,4,CDistrict calls for better safety
OL,5,Cregulations
OL,7,FAdil said that his brother Absi was
OL,8,Fwell liked throughout school and that
OL,9,Fa memorial was held to remember him.
OL,11,FHe said: "We had a memorial at school
OL,12,Fand everyone described my brother that
OL,13,Fanytime he walked in there was a light
OL,14,Fin the room.
OL,16,F"There was warmth and affection every
OL,17,Ftime he entered a room and that is now
OL,18,Fmissing from our house. He was a very
OL,19,Faffectionate person and that is
OL,20,Fsomething that is missing now.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778253065
OL,3,CBrother of boy who drowned in Lake
OL,4,CDistrict calls for better safety
OL,5,Cregulations
OL,7,F"Every time we walk past his bedroom,
OL,8,Fit still just doesn't feel real to me."
OL,10,FAdil wants to raise awareness on water
OL,11,Fsafety moving forward and to think
OL,12,Ftwice before jumping into open water.
OL,14,FHe said: "I just wanted to let
OL,15,Feveryone know and to raise the
OL,16,Fawareness of water safety.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778253065
OL,3,CBrother of boy who drowned in Lake
OL,4,CDistrict calls for better safety
OL,5,Cregulations
OL,7,F"Even if the weather is hot and the
OL,8,Fwater may look very nice to plunge in
OL,9,Fand that the water temperature is
OL,10,Fcompletely different to what the air
OL,11,Ftemperature is.
OL,13,F"If you are thinking of going for a
OL,14,Fswim, just double think before you get
OL,15,Finto the water or once you are in feel
OL,16,Fthat you are comfortable with it."
OL,18,F"I also want to raise awareness and
OL,19,Fpossibly change what safety there is
OL,20,Fat this tarn.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778253065
OL,3,CBrother of boy who drowned in Lake
OL,4,CDistrict calls for better safety
OL,5,Cregulations
OL,7,F"From what it looks like there is only
OL,8,Fa throw line at the entrance and it is
OL,9,Fa very big open body of water. I would
OL,10,Flike there to be multiple lifebelts
OL,11,Fwhere it can be seen if someone gets
OL,12,Finto difficulty.
OL,14,F"Maybe a lifebelt being there at the
OL,15,Fsite he could have been saved. I don't
OL,16,Fblame anyone as to what's happened but
OL,17,Fit would have helped if there was a
OL,18,Flifebelt and more warning sides.
OL,20,F"We don't want another family to go
OL,21,Fthrough what has happened to us."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
